# Chrome App & Extension

* [YouTube: Make A Chrome App in 5 minutes](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xgj-2etILdk) 讚!
* [What's the Difference Between a Chrome Web App and an Extension?](http://google.about.com/od/personalizegoogle/f/Whats-The-Difference-Between-A-Chrome-Web-App-And-An-Extension.htm)
 * Web apps are basically websites. They run within Chrome's browser using things like javascript and HTML, and they may not even require any downloads.
 * An extension, on the other hand, affects something global on your browser. For instance, an extension may add the ability to save items to your Amazon.com wish list. When you install the extension, that feature is available on every single site you visit, not just on Amazon.com.
